<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd">
<concept id="concept_gbn_4lv_1r">
 <title>Installation and Configuration</title>
 <shortdesc>You can install the <ph
      conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/> and start it
    manually or run it as a service. </shortdesc>
  <conbody>
    <p>If you use Cloudera Manager, you can install and administer the <ph
        conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/> through
      Cloudera Manager. For more information, see <xref
        href="CMInstall-Overview.dita#concept_nb5_c3m_25"/>.</p>
    <p>You can alternatively install a basic version of the <ph
        conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>, and add
      additional stage libraries for additional functionality as needed. For more information, see
        <xref href="BasicInstall_Overview.dita"/>.</p>
    <p>After installation, you can create additional users, customize the <ph
        conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>, and
      configure the environment. </p>
  </conbody>
</concept>
